  "text": "P values in the ANOVAs were Huynh-Feldt corrected for inhomogenities of covariance when necessary [CITATION_1] . Images are displayed by neurological convention, with left side corresponding to the left hemisphere. Effects are significant at P < 0.001 and at a cluster size of 10 or more contiguous voxels. Mean parameter estimates for the different conditions are shown for all contrasts (ordinate in arbitrary units). Error bars represent s.e.m.",
